outputs.output_descr: The Chamber of Commerce, Industry and Agriculture in Tanzania provides capacity development services to more than 17,000 members across 21 regions of the country. Its work to enhanced business growth is a critical component of the  national development strategy for growth and poverty reduction (MKUKUTA). This initiative represents an important aspect for ensuring that the Chamber is effective in  providing  support and advisory services.

project_descr: UNV Support to Strengthening of the Tanzania Chamber of Commerce, Industry and Agriculture for Innovative Business Support Services
project_title: UNV Support to TCCIA Innovative Business Support Service
